CustomField.formula: IF(OR(ISPICKVAL( Franchise_Type__c,"Commercial-Residential"), ISPICKVAL( Franchise_Type__c,"Commercial-Open Market")), Average_Users_Day_Location_OPEN__c * ((0.8383 * Single_Use_Fee_Adults__c ) + (0.1617 * Single_Use_Fee_Children__c )),0)
CustomField.label: Assumed Daily Revenue
